<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FG · 香港倉．亞洲集運中轉王</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang HK", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Noto Sans HK", sans-serif;
    background: transparent;
  }

  /* ============ Hero Container ============ */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 19 / 10;       /* 大概 380 × 200，2kg banner 一半高 */
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2856 0%, #1F3864 45%, #2c5fa0 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(31, 56, 100, 0.35);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 4% 5%;
  }

  /* 裝飾光點 */
  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 20%, rgba(201, 169, 94, 0.22) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 85%, rgba(44, 95, 160, 0.35) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #C9A95E, transparent);
  }

  /* ============ TOP ROW: Logo + Title ============ */
  .top-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }
  .fg-logo {
    width: clamp(40px, 11vw, 56px);
    height: clamp(40px, 11vw, 56px);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .fg-logo img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 50%; }

  .title-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .title-main {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 5.5vw, 1.85rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #C9A95E;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .title-sub {
    font-size: clamp(0.74rem, 2.8vw, 0.95rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  /* ============ KEYWORDS PILLS ============ */
  .keywords {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: clamp(4px, 1.5vw, 10px) 0;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }
  .keyword {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 94, 0.18);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 94, 0.55);
    color: #FFD86F;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: clamp(0.62rem, 2.1vw, 0.78rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ============ BOTTOM TAGLINE ============ */
  .bottom-row {
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }
  .punch {
    font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 3.2vw, 1.05rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
  }
  .punch-sub {
    font-size: clamp(0.6rem, 2vw, 0.7rem);
    color: #C9A95E;
    margin-top: 2px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ============ DESKTOP RESPONSIVE ============ */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      min-height: 180px;
      max-height: 220px;
      padding: 18px 32px;
    }
    .title-main { font-size: 1.85rem; }
    .title-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .keyword { font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 5px 14px; }
    .punch { font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .fg-logo { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1200px) {
    .hero { max-height: 200px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">

  <!-- TOP ROW: Logo + Hook headline -->
  <div class="top-row">
    <div class="fg-logo">
      <img src="logos/fg.png" alt="FG">
    </div>
    <div class="title-block">
      <div class="title-main">香港倉．亞洲集運中轉王</div>
      <div class="title-sub">紐西蘭香港人 · 華人社群最啱用</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- KEYWORDS -->
  <div class="keywords">
    <span class="keyword"># 海鮮乾貨</span>
    <span class="keyword"># HKTV</span>
    <span class="keyword"># 第三方平台</span>
    <span class="keyword"># 高質貨品</span>
  </div>

  <!-- BOTTOM PUNCH LINE -->
  <div class="bottom-row">
    <div class="punch">專家快線．更穩陣．速送到你手</div>
    <div class="punch-sub">FG · TWO-WAY HK ↔ NZ FORWARDING NETWORK</div>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
